# Images & Hot Reload (mandatory)

Hot reload lag on spare home was caused by `Image.network` + picsum URLs during rebuild. Follow these rules to prevent recurrence.

## 1. List/card thumbnails → AppNetworkImage

- Use [`AppNetworkImage`](lib/widgets/common/app_network_image.dart) for any image in scroll lists, cards, avatars, job thumbnails.
- [`JobThumbnail`](lib/widgets/common/job_thumbnail.dart) must delegate to `AppNetworkImage` — never `Image.network` directly.
- Avoid `NetworkImage(...)` in `CircleAvatar.backgroundImage` — use `ClipOval` + `AppNetworkImage`.

## 2. Mock data URLs

- Mock JSON must use **`mock://`** scheme (e.g. `mock://job/job-mock-1`).
- **Do not** use `picsum.photos` or other external hosts in committed mock data.
- Dev mock mode (`USE_MOCK_DATA=true`) must not trigger network fetch on reload.

## 3. Auto-scroll carousels

- Horizontal auto-scroll sections (`NewJobsSection`, `PopularJobsSection`, etc.) must use [`AutoScrollReassembleMixin`](lib/utils/auto_scroll_reassemble.dart).
- On `reassemble()`, defer restart by **800ms** — do not call `_startAutoScroll()` immediately.

## 4. Home screen ViewModels

- Tab-root screens: `didChangeDependencies` + `_providersReady` + `ChangeNotifierProvider.value` (see [`shop/home_screen.dart`](lib/screens/shop/home_screen.dart)).
- Do not put `ChangeNotifierProvider(create: ...)` in `build()` without guard.

## 5. Verification

Run before PR:

```bash
./scripts/check_no_raw_network_images.sh
flutter test test/job_thumbnail_test.dart test/spare_home_scroll_view_test.dart
```

See [`docs/HOT_RELOAD_GUIDE.md`](docs/HOT_RELOAD_GUIDE.md).
